		"Body": "<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin-bottom: 35px;\"> \n <div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia je tu a</span><span></span><span>u</span><span>ž</span><span> teraz sa star</span><span>á</span><span> o</span><span></span><span>revol</span><span>ú</span><span>ciu zdravotn</span><span>í</span><span>ctva. V</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.lenovo.com/the-human-centric-rise-of-artificial-intelligence-in-healthcare/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">prvej </span><span style=\"color: blue;\">č</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">asti</span></a></span><span></span><span>n</span><span>áš</span><span>ho poh</span><span>ľ</span><span>adu na ne</span><span>ú</span><span>prosn</span><span>ý</span><span> vstup umelej inteligencie do oblasti medic</span><span>í</span><span>ny a</span><span></span><span>wellnessu sme zistili, ak</span><span>ý</span><span>m sp</span><span>ô</span><span>sobom umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia vylep</span><span>š</span><span>uje mo</span><span>ž</span><span>nosti diagnostiky, klinickej infra</span><span>š</span><span>trukt</span><span>ú</span><span>ry a</span><span></span><span>prevent</span><span>í</span><span>vnej starostlivosti. Za</span><span>č</span><span>nite pr</span><span>á</span><span>ve tam</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.lenovo.com/envisioning-the-ai-empowered-patient-and-physician-of-the-future/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">a</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">z</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">í</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">skajte z</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">á</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">kladn</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">é</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"> inform</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">á</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">cie o</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">postojoch, nariadeniach a</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">pr</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">í</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">slu</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">š</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">n</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ý</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ch technol</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ó</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">gi</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">á</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ch</span></a></span><span> vr</span><span>á</span><span>tane inform</span><span>á</span><span>ci</span><span>í</span><span> o</span><span>&nbsp;ú</span><span>lohe spolo</span><span>č</span><span>nosti Lenovo vo v</span><span>š</span><span>etkom po</span><span>č</span><span>n</span><span>ú</span><span>c spr</span><span>á</span><span>vou nemocn</span><span>í</span><span>c a</span><span>ž</span><span> po rozvoj algoritmov.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin-top: 12pt;\"><span>V</span><span>š</span><span>etky tieto siln</span><span>é</span><span> transform</span><span>á</span><span>cie sl</span><span>úž</span><span>ia ako</span><span></span><em><span>n</span></em><em><span>á</span></em><em><span>stroje</span></em><span></span><span>pre pacientov aj poskytovate</span><span>ľ</span><span>ov </span><span>–</span><span> tento trend bude pokra</span><span>č</span><span>ova</span><span>ť</span><span> aj v</span><span>&nbsp;ď</span><span>al</span><span>š</span><span>om desa</span><span>ť</span><span>ro</span><span>čí</span><span>. Ak teda nie je pravdepodobn</span><span>é</span><span>, </span><span>ž</span><span>e umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia nahrad</span><span>í</span><span> d</span><span>ô</span><span>veryhodn</span><span>ý</span><span>ch lek</span><span>á</span><span>rov, no bude musie</span><span>ť</span><span> implementova</span><span>ť</span><span> z</span><span>á</span><span>sady ochrany osobn</span><span>ý</span><span>ch </span><span>ú</span><span>dajov pacientov, kde d</span><span>ô</span><span>jde k</span><span></span><span>ve</span><span>ľ</span><span>k</span><span>ý</span><span>m zmen</span><span>á</span><span>m?</span></p> \n  <p><strong><span>Umel</span></strong><strong><span>á</span></strong><strong><span> inteligencia o</span></strong><strong><span></span></strong><strong><span>p</span></strong><strong><span>äť</span></strong><strong><span> rokov: inteligentnej</span></strong><strong><span>š</span></strong><strong><span>ie po</span></strong><strong><span>čí</span></strong><strong><span>ta</span></strong><strong><span>č</span></strong><strong><span>e a</span></strong><strong><span></span></strong><strong><span>virtu</span></strong><strong><span>á</span></strong><strong><span>lni asistenti</span></strong></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Presu</span><span>ň</span><span>me sa pribli</span><span>ž</span><span>ne o</span><span></span><span>p</span><span>äť</span><span> rokov dopredu a</span><span></span><span>pozrime sa na to, ak</span><span>ý</span><span>m sp</span><span>ô</span><span>sobom sa odvetvie m</span><span>ôž</span><span>e zmeni</span><span>ť</span><span>. Postupn</span><span>é</span><span> skoky v</span><span></span><span>technol</span><span>ó</span><span>gi</span><span>á</span><span>ch zv</span><span>ýš</span><span>ia v</span><span>š</span><span>adepr</span><span>í</span><span>tomnos</span><span>ť</span><span> a</span><span></span><span>silu pr</span><span>í</span><span>kladov uveden</span><span>ý</span><span>ch vy</span><span>šš</span><span>ie, no kde sa preuk</span><span>áž</span><span>e skuto</span><span>č</span><span>n</span><span>á</span><span> zmena?</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Zamyslite sa nad t</span><span>ý</span><span>m, ko</span><span>ľ</span><span>ko vec</span><span>í</span><span> sa pri pr</span><span>á</span><span>ci s</span><span></span><span>virtu</span><span>á</span><span>lnym asistentom v</span><span></span><span>smartf</span><span>ó</span><span>ne deje </span><span>„</span><span>za oponou</span><span>“</span><span>. Od rozpozn</span><span>á</span><span>vania hlasu, ktor</span><span>é</span><span> sa dok</span><span>áž</span><span>e nau</span><span>č</span><span>i</span><span>ť&nbsp;</span><em><span>v</span></em><em><span>áš</span></em><span></span><span>hlas, po preh</span><span>ľ</span><span>ad</span><span>á</span><span>vanie v</span><span>ý</span><span>sledkov z</span><span></span><span>vyh</span><span>ľ</span><span>ad</span><span>á</span><span>vania na</span><span>ž</span><span>ivo s</span><span></span><span>cie</span><span>ľ</span><span>om vyu</span><span>ž</span><span>i</span><span>ť</span><span> predo</span><span>š</span><span>l</span><span>é</span><span> spr</span><span>á</span><span>vanie na zdie</span><span>ľ</span><span>anie v</span><span>ý</span><span>sledkov naprie</span><span>č</span><span> zariadeniami </span><span>–</span><span> v</span><span>äčš</span><span>ina z</span><span></span><span>n</span><span>á</span><span>s ani len netu</span><span>ší</span><span>, za </span><span>čí</span><span>m v</span><span>š</span><span>etk</span><span>ý</span><span>m stoj</span><span>í</span><span> umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia. Tease o</span><span>č</span><span>ak</span><span>á</span><span>va v</span><span></span><span>diagnostick</span><span>ý</span><span>ch technol</span><span>ó</span><span>gi</span><span>á</span><span>ch podobn</span><span>ý</span><span> fenom</span><span>é</span><span>n.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>„</span><span>Predstavte si, </span><span>ž</span><span>e idete do nemocnice na vy</span><span>š</span><span>etrenie PET alebo MR,</span><span>“</span><span> uviedol Scott Tease, v</span><span>ý</span><span>konn</span><span>ý</span><span> riadite</span><span>ľ</span><span> spolo</span><span>č</span><span>nosti Lenovo pre oblas</span><span>ť</span><span> vysokov</span><span>ý</span><span>konn</span><span>ý</span><span>ch v</span><span>ý</span><span>po</span><span>č</span><span>tov a</span><span></span><span>umelej inteligencie. </span><span>„</span><span>Sk</span><span>ô</span><span>r ako lek</span><span>á</span><span>r alebo technik skontroluje sn</span><span>í</span><span>mky, algoritmus zabezpe</span><span>čí</span><span> interpret</span><span>á</span><span>ciu </span><span>ú</span><span>dajov a</span><span></span><span>ozna</span><span>čí</span><span> ka</span><span>ž</span><span>d</span><span>ú</span><span> nezrovnalos</span><span>ť</span><span>. To ur</span><span>ý</span><span>ch</span><span>ľ</span><span>uje </span><span>ú</span><span>silie opatrovate</span><span>ľ</span><span>ov, upozor</span><span>ň</span><span>uje na probl</span><span>é</span><span>my a</span><span></span><span>pom</span><span>á</span><span>ha zabezpe</span><span>č</span><span>i</span><span>ť</span><span>, aby sa ni</span><span>č</span><span> neprehliadlo. Tieto procesy v</span><span></span><span>s</span><span>úč</span><span>asnosti preveruj</span><span>ú</span><span> regula</span><span>č</span><span>n</span><span>é</span><span> org</span><span>á</span><span>ny.</span><span>“</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"assets/build-in-contents/images/AI1.jpg\" style=\"height: 540px; width: 1024px;\"></p> \n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span>Vylep</span><span>š</span><span>en</span><span>é</span><span> mo</span><span>ž</span><span>nosti rozl</span><span>íš</span><span>enia a</span><span></span><span>anal</span><span>ý</span><span>zy umo</span><span>ž</span><span>nia vzdialen</span><span>é</span><span> skenovanie a</span><span></span><span>diagnostiku </span><span>–</span><span> dokonca aj pri mal</span><span>ý</span><span>ch a</span><span></span><span>slab</span><span>ý</span><span>ch pr</span><span>í</span><span>znakoch.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Lek</span><span>á</span><span>ri m</span><span>ôž</span><span>u by</span><span>ť</span><span> viac naklonen</span><span>í</span><span> prija</span><span>ť</span><span> tak</span><span>ý</span><span>to typ pou</span><span>ž</span><span>itia umelej inteligencie, no </span><span>č</span><span>o t</span><span>á</span><span> z</span><span>á</span><span>plava sledovac</span><span>í</span><span>ch </span><span>ú</span><span>dajov? Vyhliadky na zariadenia na sledovanie zdravia, ktor</span><span>é</span><span> v</span><span></span><span>pr</span><span>í</span><span>pade ob</span><span>á</span><span>v automaticky kontaktuj</span><span>ú</span><span> kliniku, prekvapia viacer</span><span>ý</span><span>ch.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>„</span><span>Existuj</span><span>ú</span><span> skuto</span><span>č</span><span>n</span><span>é</span><span> obavy, </span><span>ž</span><span>e person</span><span>á</span><span>l na v</span><span>ý</span><span>strahu nemus</span><span>í</span><span> v</span><span>ž</span><span>dy reagova</span><span>ť</span><span> primerane, </span><span>č</span><span>o sa v</span><span>š</span><span>ak asi len tak nezmen</span><span>í</span><span>,</span><span>“</span><span> povedal Dr. Dan Stevens, b</span><span>ý</span><span>val</span><span>ý</span><span> lek</span><span>á</span><span>r a</span><span></span><span>glob</span><span>á</span><span>lny produktov</span><span>ý</span><span> mana</span><span>žé</span><span>r spolo</span><span>č</span><span>nosti Lenovo pre oblas</span><span>ť</span><span> zdravotn</span><span>í</span><span>ctva. </span><span>„</span><span>Minim</span><span>á</span><span>lne z</span><span></span><span>kr</span><span>á</span><span>tkodob</span><span>é</span><span>ho h</span><span>ľ</span><span>adiska je pravdepodobnej</span><span>š</span><span>ie, </span><span>ž</span><span>e na vy</span><span>ž</span><span>iadanie bud</span><span>ú</span><span> k</span><span></span><span>dispoz</span><span>í</span><span>cii doplnkov</span><span>é</span><span> diagnostick</span><span>é</span><span> </span><span>ú</span><span>daje poch</span><span>á</span><span>dzaj</span><span>ú</span><span>ce z</span><span>&nbsp;ú</span><span>dajov z</span><span></span><span>pr</span><span>í</span><span>strojov nosen</span><span>ý</span><span>ch na tele.</span><span>“</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>M</span><span>ôž</span><span>eme si tie</span><span>ž</span><span> v</span><span>š</span><span>imn</span><span>úť</span><span> rast</span><span>ú</span><span>ci dopyt po </span><span>„</span><span>pohodl</span><span>í“</span><span> </span><span>–</span><span> prostredn</span><span>í</span><span>ctvom webovej lokality alebo aplik</span><span>á</span><span>cie budete ma</span><span>ť</span><span> v</span><span>š</span><span>etko na dosah ruky. Ide o</span><span></span><span>zmenu pr</span><span>í</span><span>stupu v</span><span></span><span>starostlivosti o</span><span></span><span>n</span><span>í</span><span>zkorizikov</span><span>ý</span><span>ch pacientov. V</span><span></span><span>tejto oblasti m</span><span>ôž</span><span>e umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia vies</span><span>ť</span><span> k</span><span></span><span>zdravotnej starostlivosti v</span><span>&nbsp;š</span><span>t</span><span>ý</span><span>le chatbota, kde s</span><span>é</span><span>ria cielen</span><span>ý</span><span>ch ot</span><span>á</span><span>zok spolu s</span><span></span><span>biometrick</span><span>ý</span><span>mi </span><span>ú</span><span>dajmi pom</span><span>ôž</span><span>e </span><span>ľ</span><span>u</span><span>ď</span><span>om dosta</span><span>ť</span><span> sa k</span><span></span><span>spr</span><span>á</span><span>vnemu druhu starostlivosti.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Telemedic</span><span>í</span><span>na pred rokmi, samozrejme, umo</span><span>ž</span><span>nila konzult</span><span>á</span><span>ciu s</span><span></span><span>lek</span><span>á</span><span>rom z</span><span></span><span>pohodlia domova, ale elektronick</span><span>ý</span><span> lek</span><span>á</span><span>r by mohol radik</span><span>á</span><span>lne zn</span><span>íž</span><span>i</span><span>ť</span><span> n</span><span>á</span><span>klady. Aj ke</span><span>ď</span><span> by do procesu preverovania a</span><span></span><span>schva</span><span>ľ</span><span>ovania vst</span><span>ú</span><span>pila skuto</span><span>č</span><span>n</span><span>á</span><span> osoba, rozhovor a</span><span></span><span>vyhodnotenie </span><span>ú</span><span>dajov zo strany umelej inteligencie by bezpochyby zv</span><span>ýš</span><span>ili efekt</span><span>í</span><span>vnos</span><span>ť</span><span>.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin-top: 12pt;\"><span>„</span><span>Diagnostika zo strany umelej inteligencie je komplexn</span><span>é</span><span> kontinuum,</span><span>“</span><span> povedal Stevens. </span><span>„</span><span>Rolu zohr</span><span>á</span><span>va pohodlie, hodnotenie rizika a</span><span></span><span>presnos</span><span>ť</span><span>. Pravdepodobne sa nestane, </span><span>ž</span><span>e by chatbot prevzal kontrolu nad pr</span><span>í</span><span>padmi s</span><span></span><span>nebezpe</span><span>č</span><span>n</span><span>ý</span><span>mi sympt</span><span>ó</span><span>mami.</span><span>“</span></p> \n  <p><strong><span>Umel</span></strong><strong><span>á</span></strong><strong><span> inteligencia o</span></strong><strong><span></span></strong><strong><span>10</span></strong><strong><span></span></strong><strong><span>rokov: personalizovan</span></strong><strong><span>á</span></strong><strong><span>, glob</span></strong><strong><span>á</span></strong><strong><span>lne dostupn</span></strong><strong><span>á</span></strong><strong><span> medic</span></strong><strong><span>í</span></strong><strong><span>na</span></strong></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Predpokladajme, </span><span>ž</span><span>e rozvoj navrhnut</span><span>ý</span><span>ch zmien post</span><span>ú</span><span>pi </span><span>ď</span><span>alej, za </span><span>č</span><span>o bude m</span><span>ô</span><span>c</span><span>ť</span><span> pokrok v</span><span></span><span>oblasti technol</span><span>ó</span><span>gi</span><span>í</span><span> a</span><span>&nbsp;š</span><span>ir</span><span>š</span><span>ie osvojovanie si t</span><span>ý</span><span>chto technol</span><span>ó</span><span>gi</span><span>í</span><span>.</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.lenovo.com/debunking-misconceptions-about-ai/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Myln</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">é</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"> predstavy o</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">umelej inteligencii</span></a></span><span></span><span>sa bud</span><span>ú</span><span> nar</span><span>úš</span><span>a</span><span>ť</span><span> a</span><span>&nbsp;ú</span><span>spe</span><span>š</span><span>n</span><span>é</span><span> nasadenie technol</span><span>ó</span><span>gi</span><span>í</span><span> s</span><span></span><span>podporou umelej inteligencie m</span><span>ôž</span><span>e zv</span><span>ýš</span><span>i</span><span>ť</span><span> d</span><span>ô</span><span>veru </span><span>ľ</span><span>ud</span><span>í</span><span> v</span><span>&nbsp;ž</span><span>ivot s</span><span></span><span>algoritmami. Kto by vedel poveda</span><span>ť</span><span>, do akej miery by sa zmenilo vn</span><span>í</span><span>manie </span><span>ľ</span><span>ud</span><span>í</span><span>, ak by po mest</span><span>á</span><span>ch a</span><span></span><span>dia</span><span>ľ</span><span>niciach bezprobl</span><span>é</span><span>movo jazdilo ve</span><span>ľ</span><span>a auton</span><span>ó</span><span>mnych vozidiel?</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia v</span><span></span><span>sebe v</span><span>ž</span><span>dy zah</span><span>ŕň</span><span>a aj tzv.</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/demystifying-the-black-box-that-is-ai/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">„č</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">iernu skrinku</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">“</span></a></span><span> </span><span>–</span><span> dokonalos</span><span>ť</span><span> tzv. h</span><span>ĺ</span><span>bkov</span><span>é</span><span>ho u</span><span>č</span><span>enia sa odkr</span><span>ý</span><span>va za spustenou oponou. Samozrejme, pozn</span><span>á</span><span>me vstup a</span><span></span><span>v</span><span>ý</span><span>stup, ale k</span><span></span><span>z</span><span>á</span><span>veru postupn</span><span>ý</span><span> proces umelej inteligencie dospeje len zriedka. M</span><span>ôž</span><span>e by</span><span>ť</span><span> </span><span>ť</span><span>a</span><span>ž</span><span>k</span><span>é</span><span> uveri</span><span>ť</span><span> odpovedi, ke</span><span>ď</span><span> je z</span><span>á</span><span>sadn</span><span>á</span><span> pr</span><span>á</span><span>ca skryt</span><span>á</span><span> (a</span><span></span><span>m</span><span>ôž</span><span>e obsahova</span><span>ť&nbsp;</span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.lenovo.com/how-inclusive-artificial-intelligence-is-disrupting-business-and-society/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">n</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">á</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">hodn</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">é</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"> skreslenia</span></a></span><span>).</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>V</span><span></span><span>nasleduj</span><span>ú</span><span>com desa</span><span>ť</span><span>ro</span><span>čí</span><span> pravdepodobne d</span><span>ô</span><span>vera porastie. Aj bez toho v</span><span>š</span><span>ak m</span><span>ôž</span><span>e d</span><span>ô</span><span>js</span><span>ť</span><span> k</span><span></span><span>drastickej transform</span><span>á</span><span>cii </span><span>–</span><span> do takej miery, ak</span><span>á</span><span> je v</span><span></span><span>regulovanom svete medic</span><span>í</span><span>ny mo</span><span>ž</span><span>n</span><span>á</span><span>.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Genomick</span><span>é</span><span> sekvenovanie je samo o</span><span></span><span>sebe revol</span><span>ú</span><span>ciou. Mapovanie gen</span><span>ó</span><span>mu otv</span><span>á</span><span>ra dvere do sk</span><span>ú</span><span>mania zdeden</span><span>ý</span><span>ch stavov, n</span><span>á</span><span>chylnosti k</span><span></span><span>chorob</span><span>á</span><span>m, mo</span><span>ž</span><span>nej odpovede na lie</span><span>č</span><span>bu a</span><span></span><span>nespo</span><span>č</span><span>etn</span><span>ý</span><span>ch </span><span>ď</span><span>al</span><span>ší</span><span>ch poznatkov. Tento proces v</span><span>š</span><span>ak vy</span><span>ž</span><span>aduje </span><span>č</span><span>as a</span><span></span><span>zna</span><span>č</span><span>n</span><span>ý</span><span> v</span><span>ý</span><span>kon vysokov</span><span>ý</span><span>konn</span><span>ý</span><span>ch po</span><span>čí</span><span>ta</span><span>č</span><span>ov.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Spolo</span><span>č</span><span>nos</span><span>ť</span><span> Lenovo sa ned</span><span>á</span><span>vno rozhodla pozrie</span><span>ť</span><span> sa na</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.hpcwire.com/2019/09/30/accelerating-high-performance-computing-hpc-for-population-level-genomics/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">pos</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ú</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">vanie sekvenovania na </span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ú</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">rovne popul</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">á</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">cie</span></a></span><span> </span><span>–</span><span> snaha zn</span><span>íž</span><span>i</span><span>ť</span><span> v</span><span>ý</span><span>po</span><span>č</span><span>tov</span><span>ý</span><span> </span><span>č</span><span>as 150</span><span></span><span>hod</span><span>í</span><span>n na omnoho zvl</span><span>á</span><span>dnute</span><span>ľ</span><span>nej</span><span>š</span><span>iu hodnotu. Jedno navrhovan</span><span>é</span><span> rie</span><span>š</span><span>enie, ktor</span><span>é</span><span> sa d</span><span>á</span><span> v</span><span></span><span>porovnan</span><span>í</span><span> s</span><span></span><span>in</span><span>ý</span><span>mi </span><span>š</span><span>k</span><span>á</span><span>lova</span><span>ť</span><span> r</span><span>ý</span><span>chlej</span><span>š</span><span>ie, si pri plnom gen</span><span>ó</span><span>me vy</span><span>ž</span><span>aduje iba 5,5</span><span></span><span>hodiny. Predstavte si toto </span><span>čí</span><span>slo po </span><span>ď</span><span>al</span><span>ší</span><span>ch desiatich rokoch inov</span><span>á</span><span>ci</span><span>í</span><span>.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"assets/build-in-contents/images/AI2.jpg\" style=\"height: 430px; width: 1000px;\"></p> \n  <figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\" id=\"caption-attachment-7186\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px;\"></figcaption> \n  <p>&nbsp;</p> \n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span>Superpo</span><span>čí</span><span>ta</span><span>č</span><span> MareNostrum umiestnen</span><span>ý</span><span> v</span><span></span><span>barcelonskom kostole, kde Lenovo pom</span><span>á</span><span>ha riadi</span><span>ť</span><span> siln</span><span>ý</span><span> genomick</span><span>ý</span><span> v</span><span>ý</span><span>skum.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>„Č</span><span>o keby sme dok</span><span>á</span><span>zali sekvenova</span><span>ť</span><span> v</span><span>š</span><span>etk</span><span>ý</span><span>ch a</span><span></span><span>vyvin</span><span>úť</span><span> skuto</span><span>č</span><span>ne personalizovan</span><span>ú</span><span> medic</span><span>í</span><span>nu?</span><span>“</span><span> p</span><span>ý</span><span>ta sa Tease. </span><span>„</span><span>Ak umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia a</span><span></span><span>HPC skr</span><span>á</span><span>tia v</span><span>ý</span><span>po</span><span>č</span><span>tov</span><span>ý</span><span> </span><span>č</span><span>as tak n</span><span>í</span><span>zko, doslova ka</span><span>ž</span><span>d</span><span>ý</span><span> m</span><span>ôž</span><span>e na vy</span><span>ž</span><span>iadanie z</span><span>í</span><span>ska</span><span>ť</span><span> dan</span><span>é</span><span> diagnostick</span><span>é</span><span> okno a</span><span></span><span>ur</span><span>č</span><span>i</span><span>ť</span><span> ide</span><span>á</span><span>lny a</span><span></span><span>individualizovan</span><span>ý</span><span> postup lie</span><span>č</span><span>by.</span><span>“</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Dokonca aj za t</span><span>ý</span><span>mto mas</span><span>í</span><span>vnym roz</span><span>ší</span><span>ren</span><span>í</span><span>m si Tease predstavuje svet, v</span><span></span><span>ktorom umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia zlep</span><span>š</span><span>uje pr</span><span>í</span><span>stup ku kvalitnej starostlivosti.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>„</span><span>Pacient kdeko</span><span>ľ</span><span>vek na svete bude m</span><span>ô</span><span>c</span><span>ť</span><span> zdie</span><span>ľ</span><span>a</span><span>ť</span><span> krvn</span><span>ú</span><span> vzorku spolu s</span><span></span><span>h</span><span>ĺ</span><span>bkov</span><span>ý</span><span>mi biometrick</span><span>ý</span><span>mi </span><span>ú</span><span>dajmi,</span><span>“</span><span> uv</span><span>á</span><span>dza. </span><span>„</span><span>Umel</span><span>á</span><span> inteligencia je s</span><span>úč</span><span>as</span><span>ť</span><span>ou </span><span>ú</span><span>vodnej anal</span><span>ý</span><span>zy, h</span><span>ľ</span><span>adania vzorcov, diagnostiky pacienta a</span><span></span><span>odpor</span><span>úč</span><span>ania </span><span>ď</span><span>al</span><span>ší</span><span>ch krokov. Potom sa pr</span><span>í</span><span>pad pod</span><span>ľ</span><span>a potreby eskaluje spr</span><span>á</span><span>vnemu odborn</span><span>í</span><span>kovi, ktor</span><span>ý</span><span> bude ma</span><span>ť</span><span> v</span><span>š</span><span>etky tieto inform</span><span>á</span><span>cie na dosah ruky.</span><span>“</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; text-align: left;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"assets/build-in-contents/images/AI3.jpg\" style=\"height: 621px; width: 1000px;\"></p> \n  <p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Pridajte mo</span><span>ž</span><span>nos</span><span>ť</span><span> pom</span><span>á</span><span>ha</span><span>ť</span><span> a</span><span></span><span>lie</span><span>č</span><span>i</span><span>ť</span><span> pomocou n</span><span>á</span><span>strojov s</span><span></span><span>roz</span><span>ší</span><span>renou realitou, v</span><span>ď</span><span>aka </span><span>č</span><span>omu m</span><span>ôž</span><span>e st</span><span>ú</span><span>pa</span><span>ť</span><span> kvalita a</span><span></span><span>efekt</span><span>í</span><span>vnos</span><span>ť</span><span> pri s</span><span>úč</span><span>asnom poklese n</span><span>á</span><span>kladov. Ako to bude fungova</span><span>ť</span><span> v</span><span></span><span>regula</span><span>č</span><span>nom priestore bude zauj</span><span>í</span><span>mav</span><span>é</span><span> a</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://hbr.org/2019/10/adopting-ai-in-health-care-will-be-slow-and-difficult\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">mo</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ž</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">no bolestiv</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">é</span></a></span><span> </span><span>–</span><span> hoci skor</span><span>é</span><span> prijatie n</span><span>á</span><span>m d</span><span>á</span><span>va d</span><span>ô</span><span>vody na optimizmus.</span></p> \n  <p style=\"margin-top: 12pt;\"><span>Aby bola bud</span><span>ú</span><span>cnos</span><span>ť</span><span> e</span><span>š</span><span>te jasnej</span><span>š</span><span>ia, myslite na to, </span><span>ž</span><span>e algoritmy umelej inteligencie s</span><span>ú</span><span> v</span><span>ý</span><span>konn</span><span>é</span><span> len tak, ako s</span><span>ú</span><span> dostupn</span><span>é</span><span> </span><span>ú</span><span>daje. Z</span><span>á</span><span>kladn</span><span>é</span><span> </span><span>ú</span><span>daje, ktor</span><span>é</span><span> s</span><span>ú</span><span> potrebn</span><span>é</span><span> na strojov</span><span>é</span><span> u</span><span>č</span><span>enie, vy</span><span>š</span><span>vihn</span><span>ú</span><span> anal</span><span>ý</span><span>zu big data v</span><span></span><span>zdravotn</span><span>í</span><span>ctve</span><span></span><span><span style=\"color: blue;\">do roku 2025 o</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">takmer 70</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">mili</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">á</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">rd</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">$</span></span><span>. Kto dok</span><span>áž</span><span>e predpoveda</span><span>ť</span><span>, ako sa bude umelej inteligencii v</span><span></span><span>roku 2030 dari</span><span>ť</span><span> u</span><span></span><span>pacientov aj poskytovate</span><span>ľ</span><span>ov?</span></p> \n </div> \n</div>"